= React Migration =

== Purpose ==
The '''pulse.react''' workspace supports route-by-route migration from MVC views to a React frontend while preserving URL surface compatibility.

== Stack ==
* Vite 5
* React 18
* TypeScript
* React Router
* React Query
* Axios
* Bootstrap 5

== Auth Bootstrap ==
React app bootstraps identity and API access via existing web/auth surfaces:
* user info endpoint for current identity context
* token endpoint for JWT acquisition
* JWT stored in session storage for API calls

== Migration Strategy ==
* keep route catalog aligned with Pulse.Web pages
* move page features incrementally
* preserve backend contracts during frontend swap

== Local Build Baseline ==
From the react workspace:
* install dependencies
* run production build command

Expected outcome: successful compile and bundle generation.

